Unix Installation:

	git clone git@github.com:bblodget/dotvim.git ~/.vim
	ln -s ~/.vim/exrc ~/.exrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc.unix ~/.vimrc	(for unix eol)

Windows Installation: (MINGW32 bash shell)

	git clone git@github.com:bblodget/dotvim.git ~/vimfiles
	ln -s ~/.vim/exrc ~/_exrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc.win ~/_vimrc		(for win eol)

